# Demucs / PyTorch model cache
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# The htdemucs weights (~80 MB) are downloaded by torch.hub on first
# use of the source-separation feature.  By default they live in the
# user's home directory at ~/.cache/torch/hub/checkpoints/, which is
# already outside this repo and therefore not at risk of being
# committed.  The patterns below are defensive — they catch the case
# where a developer points TORCH_HOME at the repo (e.g. for a CI box)
# and accidentally drops the multi-hundred-MB weights into the tree.
~/.cache/torch                       # documented per project policy (no-op
                                     # in standard gitignore — see note above)
.cache/torch/                        # catches TORCH_HOME=./.cache
torch_cache/                         # catches TORCH_HOME=./torch_cache
**/checkpoints/*.th                  # raw demucs model weights
